1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:22,040
Let us trigger the practice by making a long exhalation, exhale from the nose, from the chest,

2
00:00:22,040 --> 00:00:40,840
from the belly, and empty yourself of air. Allow the body to inhale freely, onto the body of empty of air.

3
00:00:40,840 --> 00:01:01,880
Exhale again from the nose, from the chest, from the belly.

4
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:33,880
Focus on exhalation in a vertical top-down from the top, from the chest. Pull the belly in to push out the air.

5
00:01:34,440 --> 00:01:48,920
Inhale as your body desires, shallow or deep.

6
00:01:48,920 --> 00:02:17,960
Keep your attention on exhalation, from the nose, from the chest, from the belly.

7
00:02:18,920 --> 00:02:41,960
With the next exhalation, bring your attention to your chest area,

8
00:02:41,960 --> 00:03:05,000
reach exhale, bring your mind lower towards the abdominal area,

9
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:34,040
from the top, from the chest, and as your exhale from the belly, bring your mind towards the center of gravity.

10
00:03:35,000 --> 00:04:00,040
Use the exhalation to help your mind lower towards the belly.

11
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:34,040
On the next exhale down, connect with your center of gravity.

12
00:04:35,000 --> 00:05:00,040
Pull the belly in, push out the air, and stay in the center of gravity.

13
00:05:35,000 --> 00:05:52,040
Prepare for the next round.

14
00:05:53,000 --> 00:06:04,120
We shall begin in three, two, one.

15
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:25,160
Exhale from the nose, from the chest, from the belly, and empty yourself of air before you inhale.

16
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:42,200
Inhale easily onto your empty body.

17
00:06:42,760 --> 00:07:03,240
Exhale from the top, from the chest, pull the belly in to push out the air.

18
00:07:04,040 --> 00:07:20,280
Allow your body to inhale easily into internal emptiness.

19
00:07:20,280 --> 00:07:43,320
Again, vertical exhalation from the top, from the chest, from the belly.

20
00:07:50,440 --> 00:08:13,320
On the next exhale down, bring your mind lower into your torso.

21
00:08:14,280 --> 00:08:34,360
With the exhale, bring your attention towards your abdominal area.

22
00:08:34,360 --> 00:09:03,400
With each exhale, bring your mind and connect with the lower abdomen towards the area of the belly.

23
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:33,400
Exhale and reach lower towards the darkness of the belly.

24
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:55,400
Reach and connect with the center of gravity.

25
00:09:56,040 --> 00:10:16,440
Pull the belly in a little more, push out the air and connect with the center.

26
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:29,480
From thought to the center of gravity.

27
00:10:30,040 --> 00:10:46,520
Let go of any breathing, just stay in the center.

28
00:10:46,520 --> 00:11:03,560
Thought comes in, exhale from the belly and connect with the center of gravity.

29
00:11:16,520 --> 00:11:45,560
Exhale and reach lower towards the darkness of the belly.

30
00:11:46,040 --> 00:11:48,600
Prepare for the next round.

31
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:57,640
We shall begin in 3, 2, 1.

32
00:11:57,640 --> 00:12:20,680
Exhale from the top, from the chest, from the belly and empty yourself of air.

33
00:12:27,640 --> 00:12:44,680
Attention and exhalation from the nose, from the chest, from the belly.

34
00:12:44,680 --> 00:13:07,720
Allow your body to inhale easily, into the internal emptiness.

35
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:41,720
From the chest, pull the belly inward to push out the air and empty yourself of air.

36
00:13:44,840 --> 00:14:05,720
With the next exhale, lower your attention towards the abdominal area.

37
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:22,760
With each exhale, bring your attention lower towards the belly.

38
00:14:22,760 --> 00:14:51,800
Pull the belly inward to push out the air and reach the center of your belly.

39
00:14:52,760 --> 00:15:19,800
Exhale and connect with the center of gravity.

40
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:29,800
Allow your body to inhale as desired.

41
00:15:29,800 --> 00:15:46,840
Continue reaching and connecting with the center of gravity with each exhale.

42
00:15:49,800 --> 00:16:18,840
From the nose, from the chest, pull the belly inward and stay in the center of gravity.

43
00:16:19,800 --> 00:16:48,840
When the floor comes in, exhale from the belly and stay in the center of gravity.

44
00:16:49,800 --> 00:17:06,840
Back to center.

45
00:17:19,800 --> 00:17:48,840
Exhale and connect with the center of gravity.

46
00:17:49,800 --> 00:18:06,840
Prepare for the next round and we begin in 3, 2, 1.

47
00:18:20,120 --> 00:18:34,840
Inhale freely, easily, onto your empty body.

48
00:18:35,400 --> 00:18:59,880
From the top, from the chest, pull the belly inward to push out the air from your body.

49
00:19:00,440 --> 00:19:14,920
Now, use your exhale to bring your mind lower to the abdominal area.

50
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:31,960
Lower abdomen towards the belly.

51
00:19:31,960 --> 00:19:59,000
With each exhale, bring your attention lower towards the center of gravity.

52
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:22,040
From thinking to centering in the point of gravity.

53
00:20:22,040 --> 00:20:49,080
Use your exhale to bring yourself lower to the belly.

54
00:20:49,080 --> 00:21:06,120
From thought to the center.

55
00:21:07,080 --> 00:21:23,160
Back to center.

56
00:21:24,120 --> 00:21:40,200
Deep in the belly.

57
00:21:40,200 --> 00:22:01,240
When thoughts arise, exhale.

58
00:22:01,240 --> 00:22:30,280
From the chest, from the belly, connect with the center of gravity.

59
00:22:31,240 --> 00:23:00,280
Exhale and center.

60
00:23:00,280 --> 00:23:17,320
From thinking to centering in the center.

61
00:23:30,280 --> 00:23:59,320
Now, prepare for round 5 in which you will be guiding yourself to connect with your center of gravity.

62
00:24:00,600 --> 00:24:17,320
Use your vertical exhalation to help you reach your center of gravity effectively.

63
00:24:18,280 --> 00:24:42,360
At some point of the practice, you may release the exhaling and any breathing and just fully connect and maintain the link with the center of gravity.

64
00:24:42,360 --> 00:24:59,400
As thoughts arise, drive them back to the center of gravity.

65
00:29:42,360 --> 00:30:07,400
At some point of the practice, you may use your vertical exhalation to help you reach your center of gravity.

66
00:30:07,960 --> 00:30:10,440
End of round 5.

67
00:30:10,440 --> 00:30:14,440
Well done.

68
00:30:14,440 --> 00:30:26,440
You have practiced in multiple rounds how to connect with your center of gravity.

69
00:30:27,000 --> 00:30:43,480
You have practiced exhalation in a vertical way to first amplify yourself of air

70
00:30:43,480 --> 00:30:49,480
and then utilize it to connect with your area of the belly.

71
00:30:49,480 --> 00:30:58,520
To establish the connection between the mind and the point of gravity.

72
00:30:58,520 --> 00:31:08,520
This way, we gradually develop the internal presence.

73
00:31:08,520 --> 00:31:24,600
The vertical link from the point of gravity all the way up to the mind.

74
00:31:24,680 --> 00:31:47,640
This way, we develop the inner presence and thereby developing the sense of being at home within yourself.

75
00:31:47,720 --> 00:32:06,680
We also enhance the internal connection within your own body and your vital centers between the mind and the center of gravity.

76
00:32:06,680 --> 00:32:29,720
Practice this in multiple rounds and in long sessions, depending on your schedule, anytime, anywhere.

